rply <- twListToDF(rply)

## eliminate all the reply other then reply to required tweet Id  
rply = rply[!rply$replyToSID > id,]
rply = rply[!rply$replyToSID < id,]
rply = rply[complete.cases(rply[,"replyToSID"]),]
